---
title: Lemon Pepper Chicken Linguine with Spinach and Parmesan
description: This pasta masterpiece really has it all. First, there are the chicken breasts, which get sliced into tender, juicy pieces that fit right in with the twirly linguine noodles. Then, you’ve got a bunch of hearty spinach to fulfill your veggie wants and needs. And when you add freshly cracked whole peppercorns and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese, you know this dish is something special indeed.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-pepper-chicken-linguine-669e3386.jpg
